source: crates/franken-node/tests/cli_subcommand_goldens.rs
---
Compatibility verification across runtimes

Usage: franken-node verify <COMMAND>

Commands:
  module         Verify module conformance against the public verifier contract
  migration      Verify migration compatibility contract output
  compatibility  Verify compatibility claims for a target profile[PATH]
  corpus         Verify corpus schema and coverage contract output
  lockstep       Compare behavior across runtimes in lockstep
  release        Verify release artifact signatures and checksums
  help           Print this message or the help of the given subcommand(s)

Options:
  -h, --help     Print help
  -V, --version  Print version
